who's a senior artist on the team.

9
00:00:40,174 --> 00:00:42,355
He's been with Guerrilla for over 15 years,

10
00:00:42,455 --> 00:00:43,976
where he worked on most of the games

11
00:00:44,137 --> 00:00:48,300
in the Killzone franchise, Horizon Zero Dawn,

12
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:50,201
and of course, Horizon Forbidden West.

13
00:00:51,242 --> 00:00:52,483
To give you the most complete look

14
00:00:52,563 --> 00:00:54,124
at the process of making these machines,

15
00:00:54,544 --> 00:00:55,785
we'll divide this talk between us.

16
00:00:58,947 --> 00:01:00,909
Let's go to the 18th of February, 2042,

17
00:01:01,649 --> 00:01:04,571
release date of Horizon Forbidden West.

18
00:01:05,476 --> 00:01:06,596
Well, it could have been.

19
